urrent_sum += (1 << j)\n                else:\n                    # We already have (1 << i) covered\n                    current_sum -= (1 << i)\n        \n        return operations\n```\n\nThis solution efficiently counts the operations needed to form the target by leveraging the properties of binary numbers and the given operations. It ensures that we only perform the minimum number of splits necessary.", "estimated_date": 1693094400000}